column5: We are walking distance to KYLE FIELD. It has many amenities including: 3 bedrooms with attached bathrooms, everything you need for kitchen/cooking, large living room with pull out couch, surround sound and big screen TV Exterior: 3 covered parking spaces, covered outdoor patio with grill, large fenced backyard with doggie door, large grassy area, dart board, fire pit, 2 dining tables.
